snippet.title: BellBottom | Official Teaser | Akshay Kumar | Vaani | Vashu Bhagnani | Huma | Lara | 02 April 2021
snippet.description:
Here’s a sneak peek into the retro themed espionage thriller Bellbottom. 

Shot in the highlands of Scotland, Pooja Entertainment's Bellbottom has Akshay Kumar in the lead playing a RAW agent on the trail of a mystery and the film’s retro theme brings back the eighties.

The film written by Aseem Arrora and Parveez Shaikh stars Vaani Kapoor as the leading lady, along with Huma Qureshi and Lara Dutta Bhupathi and is directed by Ranjit M Tewari.

Pooja Entertainment presents in association with Emmay Entertainment ‘Bellbottom’ Produced by Vashu Bhagnani, Jackky Bhagnani, Deepshikha Deshmukh, Monisha Advani, Madhu Bhojwani and Nikkhil Advani. A Pooja Entertainment production - Bellbottom is set to release in cinemas on 2nd April, 2021

Supervised by: Azeem Dayani

snippet.description:

Click here to watch all your favorite Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gqFEadNxmd8&list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu 

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Shailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Bhavya Gandhi / Raj Anadkat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalaal' to call his father 'Champaklal' (Amit Bhatt) from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in """"Gokuldham Co-operative Society"""" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - Promoolves around 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Bhavya Gandhi). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in """"Gokuldham Co-operative Society"""" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - Promoolves around 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Bhavya Gandhi). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

snippet.title: Deep Sea Fishing in Miami (Dolphin, Wahoo, Amberjacks, and Tripletail)
snippet.description:
In this episode of BlacktipH, I go fishing for dolphin (mahi-mahi), tripletail, wahoo, and amberjacks in Miami with the LandH Sport Fishing boat. The day started with us trolling planers and searching for floating debris. After catching a few bonito and mahi, we finally found some good floating debris. There was a bunch of tripletail on the debris. Both Laurel and I had a blast catching them. After catching the tripletail, we trolled planers around the debris and caught several wahoo. On our search for more floating debris, we found a huge school of mahi and boated over 20 fish. Towards the end of the day, Laurel caught the largest dolphin, a 20lb bull! On the way back into Miami, we stopped at a deep wreck and dropped down live baits for amberjack. Immediately I was hooked up to a giant! After an intense fight, I landed the 50+lb amberjack. Laurel finished the day with anther big amberjack!

snippet.localized.title: Deep Sea Fishing in Miami (Dolphin, Wahoo, Amberjacks, and Tripletail)
snippet.localized.description:
In this episode of BlacktipH, I go fishing for dolphin (mahi-mahi), tripletail, wahoo, and amberjacks in Miami with the LandH Sport Fishing boat. The day started with us trolling planers and searching for floating debris. After catching a few bonito and mahi, we finally found some good floating debris. There was a bunch of tripletail on the debris. Both Laurel and I had a blast catching them. After catching the tripletail, we trolled planers around the debris and caught several wahoo. On our search for more floating debris, we found a huge school of mahi and boated over 20 fish. Towards the end of the day, Laurel caught the largest dolphin, a 20lb bull! On the way back into Miami, we stopped at a deep wreck and dropped down live baits for amberjack. Immediately I was hooked up to a giant! After an intense fight, I landed the 50+lb amberjack. Laurel finished the day with anther big amberjack!

snippet.title: Need for Speed Hot Pursuit Remastered – Official Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Reignite the pursuit in Need for Speed™ Hot Pursuit Remastered, coming Nov. 6 on PS4, Xbox, and PC, and Nov. 13 on Switch: https://www.ea.com/games/need-for-speed/need-for-speed-hot-pursuit-remastered/news/announcing-nfs-hp-remastered

Ten years ago, Criterion Games released their critically acclaimed franchise debut Need for Speed Hot Pursuit. It introduced NFS and racing fans to the winding, open roads of Seacrest County, Criterion’s renowned feel for breakneck speed and gameplay, and the innovative Autolog system, empowering true social competition between friends. 

Ever since, we’ve heard so many stories about the triumphant moments and heated rivalries Autolog fostered. Some of which run very, very deep. Like the one between Michael and Joseph. 

Now, it’s your turn to feel the thrill of the chase and the rush of escape in NFS Hot Pursuit Remastered, arriving to PlayStation®4, Xbox One, and PC on November 6, and to Nintendo Switch™ on November 13! 

Unleash a savage sense of speed both as an outlaw and a cop in this timeless racing experience updated for today’s platforms. With cross-platform multiplayer and Autolog, enhanced visuals, all main DLC delivered at launch, and much more, this is the ultimate version of Criterion Games’ critically acclaimed Need for Speed debut.

Pre-order now: https://www.ea.com/games/need-for-speed/need-for-speed-hot-pursuit-remastered/buy
Read the full announcement: https://www.ea.com/games/need-for-speed/need-for-speed-hot-pursuit-remastered/news/announcing-nfs-hp-remastered
NFS Hot Pursuit Remastered official website: https://www.ea.com/games/need-for-speed/need-for-speed-hot-pursuit-remastered/
Follow us on Twitter: https://twitter.com/needforspeed
Follow us on Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/needforspeed/

About Need for Speed Hot Pursuit Remastered:

RACE YOUR FRIENDS WITH CROSS-PLAY AND AUTOLOG – Bolt down the winding Seacrest County roads headfirst in racing that is socially competitive at its core – now with cross-play support between PS4, Xbox One, PC, and Nintendo Switch! The groundbreaking Autolog connects you and your friends in head-to-head pursuits and races and instinctively delivers challenges based on your friends’ activities.

ENJOY LOADS OF EXTRA CONTENT AND UPDATES – Get all the additional main DLC delivered at launch including an extra six hours of gameplay and more than 30 challenges. Brand new achievements, wraps, car colors, reduced hard stops, an updated photo mode and gallery, and multiple quality of life updates create an even more well-rounded gameplay experience. 

DRIVE EXOTIC SUPERCARS WITH WEAPONS – Drive the world’s most desirable supercars on both sides of the law. Bust suspects in supercharged cop interceptors enhanced with tactical weaponry, or level the playing field with counterattacks and defensive maneuvers as an elite racer. Strategize to gain an edge over the competition, no matter what side you’re on!

CHASE AND ESCAPE TOGETHER OR SOLO – A deep and fully-defined single-player career delivers the action of both cops and racers, with a seamlessly linked multiplayer experience across all race modes. Take on friends or play through the career solo to earn Bounty and unlock new cars, weapons, and equipment.

EXPERIENCE A TIMELESS RACING GAME WITH ENHANCED VISUALS – Need for Speed™ Hot Pursuit Remastered delivers a timeless racing experience updated for today’s generation of hardware with enhanced visuals. Play in up to 4K/60 FPS and enjoy improvements such as higher-res models, shadows, and reflections, more objects and props, longer draw distance, boosted textures, more particles, and improved AA/SSAO.

snippet.title: Skip & Shannon react to Lakers Game 3 loss to Heat in NBA Finals | NBA | UNDISPUTED
snippet.description:
Jimmy Butler had a career game last night to keep the series interesting against LeBron James and the Los Angeles Lakers. With Bam Adebayo and Goran Dragic both out due to injury, Butler had a 40-point triple-double in Miami’s 115-to-104 win. LeBron and Anthony Davis only combined for 40 points. After icing the game, Butler could be heard yelling 'they’re in trouble' as he walked to the bench. Butler became the first player to have more points, rebounds and assists than LeBron in a Finals game. Hear what Skip Bayless and Shannon Sharpe have to say about Game 3 of the NBA Finals.

snippet.title: Oasis - '(What's The Story) Morning Glory?' Track by Track with Noel Gallagher [25th An...
snippet.description:
As Oasis’ seminal second album ‘(What’s The Story) Morning Glory?’ turns 25, Noel Gallagher shares his memories of writing and recording each track on the album in an exclusive new interview filmed at Rockfield Studios where the album was recorded. [Contains Strong Language]

Noel offers revealing insights into the album’s universally loved singles ‘Wonderwall’, ‘Don’t Look Back In Anger’, ‘Roll With It’, and ‘Some Might Say’ plus album tracks including ‘She’s Electric’, ‘Morning Glory’, and ‘Champagne Supernova’ which are anthems known to generations of music fans.  Noel also discusses the single’s classic B-sides, including ‘The Masterplan’, ‘Rockin’ Chair’, and ‘Step Out’.

Reflecting on how Oasis made such an iconic album in a staggeringly brief 12 days, Noel recalls: “You’re just working on instinct because you don’t second guess anything when you’re young. You’re like ‘My instinct is telling me this is great, and therefore we’ll go and we’ll do it.’”

snippet.title: Need for Speed Hot Pursuit Remastered – Official Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Reignite the pursuit in Need for Speed™ Hot Pursuit Remastered, coming Nov. 6 on PS4, Xbox, and PC, and Nov. 13 on Switch: https://www.ea.com/games/need-for-speed/need-for-speed-hot-pursuit-remastered/news/announcing-nfs-hp-remastered

Ten years ago, Criterion Games released their critically acclaimed franchise debut Need for Speed Hot Pursuit. It introduced NFS and racing fans to the winding, open roads of Seacrest County, Criterion’s renowned feel for breakneck speed and gameplay, and the innovative Autolog system, empowering true social competition between friends. 

Ever since, we’ve heard so many stories about the triumphant moments and heated rivalries Autolog fostered. Some of which run very, very deep. Like the one between Michael and Joseph. 

Now, it’s your turn to feel the thrill of the chase and the rush of escape in NFS Hot Pursuit Remastered, arriving to PlayStation®4, Xbox One, and PC on November 6, and to Nintendo Switch™ on November 13! 

Unleash a savage sense of speed both as an outlaw and a cop in this timeless racing experience updated for today’s platforms. With cross-platform multiplayer and Autolog, enhanced visuals, all main DLC delivered at launch, and much more, this is the ultimate version of Criterion Games’ critically acclaimed Need for Speed debut.

Pre-order now: https://www.ea.com/games/need-for-speed/need-for-speed-hot-pursuit-remastered/buy
Read the full announcement: https://www.ea.com/games/need-for-speed/need-for-speed-hot-pursuit-remastered/news/announcing-nfs-hp-remastered
NFS Hot Pursuit Remastered official website: https://www.ea.com/games/need-for-speed/need-for-speed-hot-pursuit-remastered/
Follow us on Twitter: https://twitter.com/needforspeed
Follow us on Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/needforspeed/

About Need for Speed Hot Pursuit Remastered:

RACE YOUR FRIENDS WITH CROSS-PLAY AND AUTOLOG – Bolt down the winding Seacrest County roads headfirst in racing that is socially competitive at its core – now with cross-play support between PS4, Xbox One, PC, and Nintendo Switch! The groundbreaking Autolog connects you and your friends in head-to-head pursuits and races and instinctively delivers challenges based on your friends’ activities.

ENJOY LOADS OF EXTRA CONTENT AND UPDATES – Get all the additional main DLC delivered at launch including an extra six hours of gameplay and more than 30 challenges. Brand new achievements, wraps, car colors, reduced hard stops, an updated photo mode and gallery, and multiple quality of life updates create an even more well-rounded gameplay experience. 

DRIVE EXOTIC SUPERCARS WITH WEAPONS – Drive the world’s most desirable supercars on both sides of the law. Bust suspects in supercharged cop interceptors enhanced with tactical weaponry, or level the playing field with counterattacks and defensive maneuvers as an elite racer. Strategize to gain an edge over the competition, no matter what side you’re on!

CHASE AND ESCAPE TOGETHER OR SOLO – A deep and fully-defined single-player career delivers the action of both cops and racers, with a seamlessly linked multiplayer experience across all race modes. Take on friends or play through the career solo to earn Bounty and unlock new cars, weapons, and equipment.

EXPERIENCE A TIMELESS RACING GAME WITH ENHANCED VISUALS – Need for Speed™ Hot Pursuit Remastered delivers a timeless racing experience updated for today’s generation of hardware with enhanced visuals. Play in up to 4K/60 FPS and enjoy improvements such as higher-res models, shadows, and reflections, more objects and props, longer draw distance, boosted textures, more particles, and improved AA/SSAO.

snippet.description:
【ROCK HDMV】
歡迎訂閱滾石唱片YouTube官方頻道 → http://bit.ly/RockRecords
#黃鴻升 #柯有倫 #竇智孔  《#扛得住》MV

Alien留給地球的最後一首友情歌
願大家一起將正能量傳出去

Alien黃鴻升「Plan B 專輯」第5首單曲
《扛得住》
黃鴻升 X 柯有倫 X 竇智孔
三位好友合唱
為後疫情時代的我們加油打氣
兄弟陪你一定可以扛得住

ALIEN黃鴻升2020專輯「Plan B」，從2019年開始籌備製作，這張專輯從最開始的A&R到專輯概念、企劃文案、拍攝ＭＶ，黃鴻升不假手他人，全部自己一手包辦，經紀人曾經擔心他手上工作太多太忙，在他寫歌詞卡關的時候，跟他說要不要乾脆找人寫詞，他思考了幾秒，肯定地說，他可以的，他自己來！

2019年6月陸續推出《蒸發》、《人生定番》、《Plan B》，時隔多月，在2020年6月再推出《我不是空笑夢》，在忙碌於主持節目、廣告代言、戲劇之外，黃鴻升對於歌手身份，已不想要只是做一個被公司規劃好的「歌手」，而是希望透過自己親手創作歌詞、寫歌曲介紹文案、拍攝ＭＶ，為自己的音樂找定位，為自己想唱的歌創造生命。

這首《扛得住》，預定在2020年9月底上架，在9月13日釋出歌名與三人的宣傳照，只是，來不及讓大家讀到他為這首歌寫的介紹文字。
所以，延續「Plan B」的精神，催生這首歌的柯有倫，以及共同合唱的竇智孔，各自為好友黃鴻升、為三人合唱的這首歌，寫下一段話，希望能夠真切傳達，關於這首歌的誕生、靈感與精神。

Alan柯有倫：
這首歌的誕生，最大的原因，其實是因爲今年疫情的關係，看到大家生活上面都遇到一些比較大的困苦，所以想要鼓勵大家，在這段時間一定要扛得住。

我們有個高爾夫球群組，前一陣子三個人常一起去高爾夫球練習場練球，因爲我們三個都希望，從今年開始，即使再忙，我們三個人都可以保持每一個月一定要下場打一場高爾夫球。
有一天，因爲這首歌寫出來，我就傳到群組裡面給他們聽，我說有沒有機會跟兩位兄弟一起唱這首歌。當然，他們兩個一聽完之後，立刻答應。
後來，我們去錄音室錄完這首歌的時候，鴻升跟我說，他希望可以把這首歌放在他的全新專輯，我跟竇哥聽了之後，當然也是一口答應。

這首歌詞曲創作的靈感，就像當年的《笨小孩》，我一直希望可以做一首是像當年的笨小孩，有三個兄弟，用一首曲子表達一種正面的力量。
我們三個人的想法應該都是一樣的，就是希望在生命裏面很簡單，然後可以做一件事情，是讓我們三個人都覺得是很正面，然後很快樂的。
在這個打拼的路上，我們三個兄弟互相都看到彼此的辛苦，也看到彼此的堅持與執着。希望能用這種心境，去鼓勵所有不管是遇到困難、或者是遇到挫折的人。

想跟鴻升說的就是，這一趟太短了，下輩子我們再做朋友、我們再做兄弟，有你在身邊一起並肩作戰，是我這一輩子最驕傲最光榮的事。

竇智孔：
9月18日.晚上18:42分
在收到滾石發來的信息後，
我想這是你搞的鬼吧！
我崩潰了。
你..太賤了....
我會在我的隱形筆記本裡註記的。
然後，
我回頭翻著簡訊，
我找到了我們兄弟情開始的地方。
我承認我不是一個好相處的人。
但你的舉動讓我決定把牆全打開了。
簡訊裡
我：我們外景提來賓，不知道你會不會願意來幫忙。
你：只要你需要我的，我就盡全力幫忙，ok!（你就是這麼可愛）
我想緣分就是這麼簡單
然後，我們完成了一些回憶，
當然我們還有很多約好的計畫……

沒事，兄弟，再見。
兄弟我扛得住！
我們保持聯絡⋯。

⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯

『無論是逼不得已，或是因為是退卻而放棄、
無論如何，儘管緊緊擁抱遺憾，時間仍舊不可逆。
時針分針秒針，前進的頻率不同， 方向卻總是一致。
時針不會為了你而開始逆轉，但你可以順著時間的流，釐清造成的不甘的源頭，
毫無懸念的繼續順時針前行。』

—截自Alien黃鴻升，2019/11/28 寫於「Plan B」專輯概念

計劃趕不上變化、時間也無法倒轉，
面對遺憾和困難，請讓 扛得住 成為定番。

這是他留給地球的最後一首友情歌，只要有音樂陪伴，相信大家一定扛得住；願每個人都永遠記得鴻升帶來的美好，一起將他的正能量傳遞出去。

snippet.title: Joe Biden and Donald Trump's fiery first debate—Here are the highlights
snippet.description:
President Donald Trump and former Vice President Joe Biden got heated during their first chance to challenge each other face to face during the first presidential debate. Hardly a minute went by without one of the candidates interrupting the other, whether on the coronavirus, the Supreme Court or the economy. Even the moderator, Fox News' Chris Wallace, couldn't always stay above the fray. For access to live and exclusive video from CNBC subscribe to CNBC PRO: https://cnb.cx/2NGeIvi 

President Donald Trump and former Vice President Joe Biden had their first chance to challenge each other face to face. They did — a lot.

Hardly a minute went by in the 90-minute brawl without one of the candidates angrily interrupting the other, whether on the coronavirus pandemic, the Supreme Court, the economy or anything else, including each other’s families.

“Will you shut up, man?” Biden snapped at Trump at one point. “You’re the worst president America has ever had,” he said later.

“China ate your lunch,” Trump shot back at Biden during questions on the economy.

Even the moderator, Fox News’ Chris Wallace, couldn’t always stay above the fray.

“I hate to raise my voice, but why shouldn’t I be different than the two of you?” the exasperated host said at one point.

Here are the highlights.

snippet.title: HIGHLIGHTS | Liverpool vs Arsenal (3-1) | Premier League
snippet.description:
Our winning start to the season is over after Liverpool fought back to beat us at Anfield.
 
A bizarre goal from Alex Lacazette saw us lead the champions and lay the foundations for a memorable result. But our advantage lasted just two minutes as Sadio Mane and Andy Robertson struck to turn the tide in Liverpool's favour.

Diogo Jota then put the game to bed moments before full time with a crisp finish into the bottom left-hand corner. 

#arsenal #highlights #premierleague

snippet.title: President Trump and Melania Trump test positive for Covid-19
snippet.description:
President Donald Trump and first lady Melania Trump tested positive for coronavirus, the President announced early Friday morning, an extraordinary development coming months into a global pandemic and in the final stretch of his reelection campaign.
"Tonight, @FLOTUS and I tested positive for COVID-19. We will begin our quarantine and recovery process immediately. We will get through this TOGETHER!" Trump tweeted shortly before 1 am Friday.
In a memo issued to reporters around 1 a.m. ET, the President's physician, Navy Commander Dr. Sean Conley, wrote he received confirmation of the positive tests on Thursday evening.
"The President and First Lady are both well at this time, and they plan to remain at home within the White House during their convalescence," Conley wrote.

#Covid #Trump #CNN #News

snippet.title: Joe Biden and President Donald Trump spar in first debate: 'Will you shut up, man?'
snippet.description:
President Donald Trump and former Vice President Joe Biden face off in the first presidential debate Tuesday night, hosted by Case Western Reserve University in Cleveland, Ohio. For access to live and exclusive video from CNBC subscribe to CNBC PRO: https://cnb.cx/2NGeIvi 

President Donald Trump and former Vice President Joe Biden had their first chance to challenge each other face to face. They did — a lot.

Hardly a minute went by in the 90-minute brawl without one of the candidates angrily interrupting the other, whether on the coronavirus pandemic, the Supreme Court, the economy or anything else, including each other’s families.

“Will you shut up, man?” Biden snapped at Trump at one point. “You’re the worst president America has ever had,” he said later.

“China ate your lunch,” Trump shot back at Biden during questions on the economy.

Even the moderator, Fox News’ Chris Wallace, couldn’t always stay above the fray.

“I hate to raise my voice, but why shouldn’t I be different than the two of you?” the exasperated host said at one point.

snippet.title: Joe Biden and President Donald Trump discuss Covid-19 in first debate
snippet.description:
President Donald Trump and former Vice President Joe Biden face off in the first presidential debate Tuesday night, hosted by Case Western Reserve University in Cleveland, Ohio. For access to live and exclusive video from CNBC subscribe to CNBC PRO: https://cnb.cx/2NGeIvi 

Biden swiped at Trump over the president’s early handling of the coronavirus, alleging that the administration started to inform the public of the disease’s severity only when it hit the stock market.

“Do you believe for a moment what he’s telling you in light of all the lies he’s told you about the whole issue relating to Covid?” Biden asked. “He still hasn’t even acknowledged that he knew this was happening — knew how dangerous it would be back in February — and he didn’t even tell you.”

“He panicked, or just looked at the stock market, one of the two,” Biden added. “Because guess what? A lot of people died and a lot more are going to die unless he gets a lot smarter or a lot quicker.”

snippet.title: Joe Biden and Donald Trump's fiery first debate—Here are the highlights
snippet.description:
President Donald Trump and former Vice President Joe Biden got heated during their first chance to challenge each other face to face during the first presidential debate. Hardly a minute went by without one of the candidates interrupting the other, whether on the coronavirus, the Supreme Court or the economy. Even the moderator, Fox News' Chris Wallace, couldn't always stay above the fray. For access to live and exclusive video from CNBC subscribe to CNBC PRO: https://cnb.cx/2NGeIvi 

President Donald Trump and former Vice President Joe Biden had their first chance to challenge each other face to face. They did — a lot.

Hardly a minute went by in the 90-minute brawl without one of the candidates angrily interrupting the other, whether on the coronavirus pandemic, the Supreme Court, the economy or anything else, including each other’s families.

“Will you shut up, man?” Biden snapped at Trump at one point. “You’re the worst president America has ever had,” he said later.

“China ate your lunch,” Trump shot back at Biden during questions on the economy.

Even the moderator, Fox News’ Chris Wallace, couldn’t always stay above the fray.

“I hate to raise my voice, but why shouldn’t I be different than the two of you?” the exasperated host said at one point.

Here are the highlights.

snippet.title: The Infinite Pattern That Never Repeats
snippet.description:
Simples rules of geometry meant that 5-fold symmetry was impossible as were crystals without a periodic structure. This turns out to be wrong. Thanks to LastPass for sponsoring a portion of this video. Click here to start using LastPass: https://ve42.co/LPs

Huge thanks to Prof. Paul Steinhardt for the interview on this topic. Check out his book ‘The Second Kind of Impossible’

If you'd like to learn more about Penrose tilings, go check out "Penrose Tiles to Trapdoor Ciphers" by Martin Gardener, which helped my research for this video.

Filmed by Gene Nagata (Potato Jet on YouTube)
Animations by Iván Tello and Jonny Hyman
Editing, Coloring, Music & Audio mastering by Jonny Hyman

Prague scenes filmed in 2012.
Special thanks to Raquel Nuno for helping with the tilings!

snippet.title: President Trump and Melania Trump test positive for Covid-19
snippet.description:
President Donald Trump and first lady Melania Trump tested positive for coronavirus, the President announced early Friday morning, an extraordinary development coming months into a global pandemic and in the final stretch of his reelection campaign.
"Tonight, @FLOTUS and I tested positive for COVID-19. We will begin our quarantine and recovery process immediately. We will get through this TOGETHER!" Trump tweeted shortly before 1 am Friday.
In a memo issued to reporters around 1 a.m. ET, the President's physician, Navy Commander Dr. Sean Conley, wrote he received confirmation of the positive tests on Thursday evening.
"The President and First Lady are both well at this time, and they plan to remain at home within the White House during their convalescence," Conley wrote.

#Covid #Trump #CNN #News

snippet.title: Israel Adesanya's Coach: Paulo Costa Win, Jon Jones Twitter Beef, Jan Blachowicz, Weidman, Chimaev

snippet.title: Roda Viva | Luiza Helena Trajano | 05/10/2020
snippet.description:
O Roda Viva entrevista a empresária Luiza Helena Trajano.

Com a experiência de quem criou um conglomerado de mais de mil lojas físicas, além do comércio virtual, e que emprega 40 mil funcionários, ela tem assumido um papel cada vez mais relevante no plano social. Após o início da crise do Coronavirus, foi uma das primeiras a aderir ao movimento “Não Demita”, que reúne mais de mil empresas comprometidas com a garantia de emprego para seus funcionários.

Em suas palestras e entrevistas, tem defendido maior consciência do empresariado diante do que chama de aspectos selvagens do capitalismo. Mais recentemente, a Magazine Luiza provocou polêmica ao anunciar um programa de trainees voltado apenas para jovens negros. Por conta disso chegou a ser acusada de discriminação. Em 2020, Luiza Trajano assumiu o oitavo lugar na lista dos bilionários da revista Forbes, a única mulher entre os Top Ten. 

#RodaViva

snippet.title: Gusttavo Lima previu que essa música seria sucesso  | Cortes do Prosa
snippet.description:
Neste vídeo, o cantor e compositor Tierry fala sobre sua relação com Gusttavo Lima.
Algumas músicas de Tierry que fizeram e fazem muito sucesso:
Hakearam-me, HB20, Cracudo, Motoboy do delivery, Oh Rita, entre outras.

Tierry conta como conheceu Gusttavo Lima.
Curiosidade: Gusttavo Lima recentemente fez live na Amazônia e realizou o boteco sunset.

Quem é Tierry, compositor e cantor? Sim!
Tierry é percebido na indústria da música como compositor versátil, um coringa, capaz de criar hits para artistas de vários estilos.

Pra sempre ter uma boa prosa sertaneja no YouTube, se INSCREVA no nosso canal clicando nesse link: http://bit.ly/ProsaSertanejeiro

 + Quanto mais gente, melhor a prosa!

Meu instagram: @renatosertanejeiro

Prosa Sertaneja é um canal criado para o formato de PodCast voltado para a música Sertaneja. Um projeto idealizado por Renato Sertanejeiro.

snippet.title: ANAVITÓRIA - Cecília
snippet.description:
Clique e ouça: https://umusicbrazil.lnk.to/OTempoEAgoraYD
 
SIGA O DUO ANAVITÓRIA:
https://www.facebook.com/anavitoriatocantins
https://www.instagram.com/oanavitoria
https://twitter.com/oanavitoria
 
Cecília
(Ana Caetano) 
Teu olho despencou de mim 
Não reconheço a tua voz 
Não sei mais te chamar de amor 
Não ouvirão falar de nós 
A gente se esqueceu, amor: 
Certeza não existe não 
E a pressa que você deixou 
Não vem em minha direção 
Parece que o tempo todo 
A gente nem percebeu 
Que aqui não dava pé não 
Que tua amarra no meu peito não se deu 
Te vi escapar das minhas mãos 
Eu te busquei, mas 
Não vi teu rosto não 
Eu te busquei, mas 
Não vi teu rosto... 
Não 
Ausência quer me sufocar 
Saudade é privilégio teu 
E eu canto pra aliviar 
O pranto que ameaça 
Difícil é ver que tu não há 
Em canto algum eu posso ver 
Nem telhado, nem sala de estar 
Rodei tudo, não achei você

snippet.title: 140 MIL reais por uma falha no Instagram aos 14 anos de idade! - Conversei com Andres Alonso
snippet.description:
Bati um papo com o Andres Alonso, o jovem brasileiro de apenas 14 anos de idade que ganhou a recompensa de 25mil dólares  (mais de 140mil reais na cotação atual!)  por ter descoberto uma vulnerabilidade no Instagram.
Durante nossa conversa, ele nos contou todo o processo da descoberta da falha, como foi reportar, e como foi receber essa premiação, além de toda a sua trajetória em tecnologia e hacking.
Você vai se surpreender com os conhecimentos e a postura de hacker ético dele, mesmo com tão pouca idade. Sem dúvidas um orgulho pra nós, brasileiros.

snippet.title: TUDO SOBRE O PIX: 6 respostas para entender o novo sistema do BC de um jeito simples e prático

snippet.title: Need for Speed Hot Pursuit Remastered – Official Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Reignite the pursuit in Need for Speed™ Hot Pursuit Remastered, coming Nov. 6 on PS4, Xbox, and PC, and Nov. 13 on Switch: https://www.ea.com/games/need-for-speed/need-for-speed-hot-pursuit-remastered/news/announcing-nfs-hp-remastered

Ten years ago, Criterion Games released their critically acclaimed franchise debut Need for Speed Hot Pursuit. It introduced NFS and racing fans to the winding, open roads of Seacrest County, Criterion’s renowned feel for breakneck speed and gameplay, and the innovative Autolog system, empowering true social competition between friends. 

Ever since, we’ve heard so many stories about the triumphant moments and heated rivalries Autolog fostered. Some of which run very, very deep. Like the one between Michael and Joseph. 

Now, it’s your turn to feel the thrill of the chase and the rush of escape in NFS Hot Pursuit Remastered, arriving to PlayStation®4, Xbox One, and PC on November 6, and to Nintendo Switch™ on November 13! 

Unleash a savage sense of speed both as an outlaw and a cop in this timeless racing experience updated for today’s platforms. With cross-platform multiplayer and Autolog, enhanced visuals, all main DLC delivered at launch, and much more, this is the ultimate version of Criterion Games’ critically acclaimed Need for Speed debut.

Pre-order now: https://www.ea.com/games/need-for-speed/need-for-speed-hot-pursuit-remastered/buy
Read the full announcement: https://www.ea.com/games/need-for-speed/need-for-speed-hot-pursuit-remastered/news/announcing-nfs-hp-remastered
NFS Hot Pursuit Remastered official website: https://www.ea.com/games/need-for-speed/need-for-speed-hot-pursuit-remastered/
Follow us on Twitter: https://twitter.com/needforspeed
Follow us on Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/needforspeed/

About Need for Speed Hot Pursuit Remastered:

RACE YOUR FRIENDS WITH CROSS-PLAY AND AUTOLOG – Bolt down the winding Seacrest County roads headfirst in racing that is socially competitive at its core – now with cross-play support between PS4, Xbox One, PC, and Nintendo Switch! The groundbreaking Autolog connects you and your friends in head-to-head pursuits and races and instinctively delivers challenges based on your friends’ activities.

ENJOY LOADS OF EXTRA CONTENT AND UPDATES – Get all the additional main DLC delivered at launch including an extra six hours of gameplay and more than 30 challenges. Brand new achievements, wraps, car colors, reduced hard stops, an updated photo mode and gallery, and multiple quality of life updates create an even more well-rounded gameplay experience. 

DRIVE EXOTIC SUPERCARS WITH WEAPONS – Drive the world’s most desirable supercars on both sides of the law. Bust suspects in supercharged cop interceptors enhanced with tactical weaponry, or level the playing field with counterattacks and defensive maneuvers as an elite racer. Strategize to gain an edge over the competition, no matter what side you’re on!

CHASE AND ESCAPE TOGETHER OR SOLO – A deep and fully-defined single-player career delivers the action of both cops and racers, with a seamlessly linked multiplayer experience across all race modes. Take on friends or play through the career solo to earn Bounty and unlock new cars, weapons, and equipment.

EXPERIENCE A TIMELESS RACING GAME WITH ENHANCED VISUALS – Need for Speed™ Hot Pursuit Remastered delivers a timeless racing experience updated for today’s generation of hardware with enhanced visuals. Play in up to 4K/60 FPS and enjoy improvements such as higher-res models, shadows, and reflections, more objects and props, longer draw distance, boosted textures, more particles, and improved AA/SSAO.

snippet.title: In seiner Videobotschaft rutscht Donald Trump ein verräterischer Satz heraus: "Habe viel gelernt"
snippet.description:
#Trump #Corona #USA 
Der mit Corona infizierte US-Präsident Donald Trump hatte am Sonntag ein Video in den sozialen Netzwerken veröffentlicht, in dem er zugab, einiges über Corona gelernt zu haben. Das würde bedeuten, dass der Präsident zuvor wenig über das Virus wusste, an dem bereits über 200.000 Amerikaner gestorben sind.
Für eine kleine Spritztour im Wagen war er offenbar schon wieder fit genug. Trump hat am Sonntag für kurze Zeit sein Krankenhaus in der Nähe der Hauptstadt Washington D.C. verlassen, um aus dem Auto heraus einer Gruppe von Anhängern zuzuwinken.
Zuvor hatte Trump auf Twitter ein Video veröffentlicht, auf dem er über seinen Gesundheitszustand spricht – und über seine Zeit im Krankenhaus. Vor allem eine Passage stach aus Trumps kurzer Ansprache heraus.
“Es war eine sehr interessante Reise, ich habe viel über das Coronavirus gelernt. Ich habe es gelernt, indem ich eine richtige Lektion erhalten habe. Das ist die echte Lektion, nicht die Lektion, die man aus Büchern erhält. Und ich kapiere es, und ich verstehe es. Und es ist eine sehr interessante Sache, ich werde euch noch davon berichten.“
In den US-Medien sorgte der Satz für Schlagzeilen. Hatte Trump gerade eingeräumt, dass er sich erst dann ernsthaft mit dem Coronavirus auseinandergesetzte, nachdem er sich selbst damit infiziert hatte? Seinem riesigen Expertenstab und mehr als 200.000 toten Amerikanern zum Trotz?
Die Kritiker stürzten sich sofort auf den verräterischen Satz des US-Präsidenten. „Das ist verheerend“, schrieb Antony Blinken, Berater des demokratischen Präsidentschaftskandidaten Joe Biden, auf Twitter. „Der Zeitpunkt, um das zu lernen, war bevor wir 200.000 Tote hatten, nicht wenn es dich selbst betrifft. Wir wünschen dir alles Gute, aber wir wünschen uns auch, du hättest deine Arbeit gemacht.“

snippet.title: Joe will nur eins: RACHE AN THEO! 😡😱😰 | Berlin - Tag & Nacht #2293
snippet.description:
Joe packt es einfach nicht, dass Theo frei draußen herumläuft! Auch seine Schwester Paula kommt nicht mehr klar auf Theos Art!  Warum kann er nicht dazu stehen, dass er verantwortlich für den Brand in der WG war und Peggys Verbrennungen?! Es wird sehr gefährlich für Theo!

Die gescriptete Reality-Soap „Berlin - Tag & Nacht“ zeigt die coolste WG Berlins, mit Themen wie  Freundschaft, Liebe,  Eifersucht, Affären, Glück, Freude und Leiden. Wie im echten Leben eben!
Alte wie neue WG-Bewohner, u. a. Ole, Joe, Peggy, Krätze, Schmidti, Eule, Basti Paula, Piet, Milla, Leon und viele weitere, zeigen dir ihr Leben in Berlin, der bunten Metropole Deutschlands. Sie nehmen dich mit in ihre Wohngemeinschaften, auf ihre Arbeitsplätze, in den Club Matrix, den Friseursalon „Schnitte“ sowie die Bar LA 14. Auch ein Tattoostudio und das Fitnessstudio Body Burn gehören zu den unterschiedlichen und wechselnden Handlungsorten der Serie. Die Großstadt-Soap „Berlin – Tag & Nacht“ ist nicht zuletzt deshalb so beliebt, weil sie die Bewohner der WGs im Ringen mit alltäglichen Problemen zeigt: Affäre und Eifersucht, Erfolgsdruck im Beruf sowie viele zwischenmenschliche Konflikte. 

"Berlin - Tag & Nacht" läuft Montag bis Freitag um 19:05 Uhr bei RTLZWEI.

snippet.title: Need for Speed Hot Pursuit Remastered – Official Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Reignite the pursuit in Need for Speed™ Hot Pursuit Remastered, coming Nov. 6 on PS4, Xbox, and PC, and Nov. 13 on Switch: https://www.ea.com/games/need-for-speed/need-for-speed-hot-pursuit-remastered/news/announcing-nfs-hp-remastered

Ten years ago, Criterion Games released their critically acclaimed franchise debut Need for Speed Hot Pursuit. It introduced NFS and racing fans to the winding, open roads of Seacrest County, Criterion’s renowned feel for breakneck speed and gameplay, and the innovative Autolog system, empowering true social competition between friends. 

Ever since, we’ve heard so many stories about the triumphant moments and heated rivalries Autolog fostered. Some of which run very, very deep. Like the one between Michael and Joseph. 

Now, it’s your turn to feel the thrill of the chase and the rush of escape in NFS Hot Pursuit Remastered, arriving to PlayStation®4, Xbox One, and PC on November 6, and to Nintendo Switch™ on November 13! 

Unleash a savage sense of speed both as an outlaw and a cop in this timeless racing experience updated for today’s platforms. With cross-platform multiplayer and Autolog, enhanced visuals, all main DLC delivered at launch, and much more, this is the ultimate version of Criterion Games’ critically acclaimed Need for Speed debut.

Pre-order now: https://www.ea.com/games/need-for-speed/need-for-speed-hot-pursuit-remastered/buy
Read the full announcement: https://www.ea.com/games/need-for-speed/need-for-speed-hot-pursuit-remastered/news/announcing-nfs-hp-remastered
NFS Hot Pursuit Remastered official website: https://www.ea.com/games/need-for-speed/need-for-speed-hot-pursuit-remastered/
Follow us on Twitter: https://twitter.com/needforspeed
Follow us on Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/needforspeed/

About Need for Speed Hot Pursuit Remastered:

RACE YOUR FRIENDS WITH CROSS-PLAY AND AUTOLOG – Bolt down the winding Seacrest County roads headfirst in racing that is socially competitive at its core – now with cross-play support between PS4, Xbox One, PC, and Nintendo Switch! The groundbreaking Autolog connects you and your friends in head-to-head pursuits and races and instinctively delivers challenges based on your friends’ activities.

ENJOY LOADS OF EXTRA CONTENT AND UPDATES – Get all the additional main DLC delivered at launch including an extra six hours of gameplay and more than 30 challenges. Brand new achievements, wraps, car colors, reduced hard stops, an updated photo mode and gallery, and multiple quality of life updates create an even more well-rounded gameplay experience. 

DRIVE EXOTIC SUPERCARS WITH WEAPONS – Drive the world’s most desirable supercars on both sides of the law. Bust suspects in supercharged cop interceptors enhanced with tactical weaponry, or level the playing field with counterattacks and defensive maneuvers as an elite racer. Strategize to gain an edge over the competition, no matter what side you’re on!

CHASE AND ESCAPE TOGETHER OR SOLO – A deep and fully-defined single-player career delivers the action of both cops and racers, with a seamlessly linked multiplayer experience across all race modes. Take on friends or play through the career solo to earn Bounty and unlock new cars, weapons, and equipment.

EXPERIENCE A TIMELESS RACING GAME WITH ENHANCED VISUALS – Need for Speed™ Hot Pursuit Remastered delivers a timeless racing experience updated for today’s generation of hardware with enhanced visuals. Play in up to 4K/60 FPS and enjoy improvements such as higher-res models, shadows, and reflections, more objects and props, longer draw distance, boosted textures, more particles, and improved AA/SSAO.

snippet.title: Deutschrap-Doku: Straight Outta Bornheim mit Celo & Abdi | DASDING
snippet.description:
Frankfurt Bornheim – der Stadtteil ist in fester Hand von dem Rap-Duo Celo & Abdi. Neben dem FSV Frankfurt, Gentrifizierung, einem vielseitigen kulturellen Leben und der Nähe zur EZB haben die beiden hier die Base von ihrem Label 385idéal aufgeschlagen. Wie keine anderen vereinen Celo & Abdi ernste Diaspora-Themen, mit Humor und Strassen-Erfahrungen. Celo & Abdi sind fest verwurzelt in Bornheim, haben die Multilingualität aka Hinterhofjargon in Deutschland salonfähig gemacht und stehen kurz davor ihr nächstes Album – Mietwagentape 2 – rauszubringen. Sie verfügen über einen umfangreichen Blick auf die Frankfurter Rap Vergangenheit – haben aber auch die Zukunft fest im Blick – mit Olexesh und Nimo sind zwei starke Rapper auf 385idéal gesigned. 


Unser Host Zino trifft Celo & Abdi und lässt sich von ihnen durch den Stadtteil führen. Er will wissen, wie sehr die Hood mit deren Rap-Musik zusammenhängt. Die Tour geht vom FSV Stadion, über der Geburtsstätte des Hinterhof-Jargons hin zum Platz wo sie ihr erstes HDF (Halt die Fresse) gedreht haben und endet in ihrem Lieblingscafe an der Konsti. Es wird mehr als deutlich, dass Celo & Abdi das Viertel, die Menschen, Rap-Musik und den Fußball in Bornheim lieben. Straight Outta Bornheim – hier zeigt sich für Zino, wie aus Hood-Liebe Rap-Musik wird. 


Abonnieren und Glocke anmachen nicht vergessen! Schreibt uns in die Kommentare, wer für dich der Rap-Ehrenbürger von Frankfurt ist.

#Celo & Abdi #Frankfurt Bornheim #MWT2

Im Song-Tindern swipet sich Johannes mit seinen Interview-Gästen durch eine für jeden Künstler ganz spezielle Musik-Auswahl. Die Stars müssen sich entscheiden: Grünes Herz oder rotes X? Im Scratched-Interview bringt Walerija die gelbe Lyrics-Box mit und die Musiker kratzen nach und nach ihre Songtexte, Kommentare, Bilder und Gewinne frei. Dazu gibt es immer die passenden Fragen. snippet.title: Announcement of the 2020 Nobel Prize in Physics
snippet.description:
The Nobel Prize in Physics 2020 was divided, one half awarded to Roger Penrose "for the discovery that black hole formation is a robust prediction of the general theory of relativity", the other half jointly to Reinhard Genzel and Andrea Ghez "for the discovery of a supermassive compact object at the centre of our galaxy."

The announcement was made at the Royal Swedish Academy of Sciences in Stockholm.

#nobelprize
